<Link id="l00654" /><CodeLine lineNumber="654"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00655" /><CodeLine lineNumber="655"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// Tracker for what values are in machine locations. Listens to the Things</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00656" /><CodeLine lineNumber="656"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// being Done by various instructions, and maintains a table of what machine</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00657" /><CodeLine lineNumber="657"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// locations have what values (as defined by a ValueIDNum).</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00658" /><CodeLine lineNumber="658"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00659" /><CodeLine lineNumber="659"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// There are potentially a much larger number of machine locations on the</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00660" /><CodeLine lineNumber="660"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// target machine than the actual working-set size of the function. On x86 for</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00661" /><CodeLine lineNumber="661"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// example, we&#39;re extremely unlikely to want to track values through control</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00662" /><CodeLine lineNumber="662"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// or debug registers. To avoid doing so, MLocTracker has several layers of</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00663" /><CodeLine lineNumber="663"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// indirection going on, described below, to avoid unnecessarily tracking</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00664" /><CodeLine lineNumber="664"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// any location.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00665" /><CodeLine lineNumber="665"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00666" /><CodeLine lineNumber="666"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// Here&#39;s a sort of diagram of the indexes, read from the bottom up:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00667" /><CodeLine lineNumber="667"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00668" /><CodeLine lineNumber="668"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///           Size on stack   Offset on stack</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00669" /><CodeLine lineNumber="669"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///                 \\              /</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00670" /><CodeLine lineNumber="670"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///          Stack Idx (Where in slot is this?)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00671" /><CodeLine lineNumber="671"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///                         /</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00672" /><CodeLine lineNumber="672"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///                        /</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00673" /><CodeLine lineNumber="673"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// Slot Num (%stack.0)   /</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00674" /><CodeLine lineNumber="674"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// FrameIdx =&gt; SpillNum /</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00675" /><CodeLine lineNumber="675"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///              \\      /</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00676" /><CodeLine lineNumber="676"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///           SpillID (int)   Register number (int)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00677" /><CodeLine lineNumber="677"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///                      \\       /</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00678" /><CodeLine lineNumber="678"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///                      LocationID =&gt; LocIdx</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00679" /><CodeLine lineNumber="679"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///                                |</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00680" /><CodeLine lineNumber="680"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///                       LocIdx =&gt; ValueIDNum</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00681" /><CodeLine lineNumber="681"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00682" /><CodeLine lineNumber="682"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// The aim here is that the LocIdx =&gt; ValueIDNum vector is just an array of</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00683" /><CodeLine lineNumber="683"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// values in numbered locations, so that later analyses can ignore whether the</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00684" /><CodeLine lineNumber="684"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// location is a register or otherwise. To map a register / spill location to</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00685" /><CodeLine lineNumber="685"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// a LocIdx, you have to use the (sparse) LocationID =&gt; LocIdx map. And to</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00686" /><CodeLine lineNumber="686"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// build a LocationID for a stack slot, you need to combine identifiers for</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00687" /><CodeLine lineNumber="687"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// which stack slot it is and where within that slot is being described.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00688" /><CodeLine lineNumber="688"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00689" /><CodeLine lineNumber="689"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// Register mask operands cause trouble by technically defining every register;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00690" /><CodeLine lineNumber="690"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// various hacks are used to avoid tracking registers that are never read and</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00691" /><CodeLine lineNumber="691"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// only written by regmasks.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00692" /><CodeLine lineNumber="692" lineLink="/docs/api/classes/livedebugvalues/mloctracker"><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">class </span><span class="doxyHighlight"><a href="/docs/api/classes/livedebugvalues/mloctracker/#ae118b50388837cac4d807896b91f111e">MLocTracker</a> &#123;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00693" /><CodeLine lineNumber="693"><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">public</span><span class="doxyHighlight">:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00694" /><CodeLine lineNumber="694" lineLink="/docs/api/classes/livedebugvalues/mloctracker/#ae1a29742ce2fd47f4b4769dfe5a44f9e"><span class="doxyHighlight">  <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/machinefunction">MachineFunction</a> &amp;<a href="/docs/api/classes/livedebugvalues/mloctracker/#ae1a29742ce2fd47f4b4769dfe5a44f9e">MF</a>;</span></CodeLine>
